{"tid":1500043,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"fb專頁：英領館職員鄭文傑已獲釋回港","createTime":"2019-08-24T02:55:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T05:45:00.000Z","uid":13468,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"710497f3375ad226bf913f87fe8a7bcfe2959db1","tid":1500043,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T02:55:52.000Z","msg":"fb專頁：英領館職員鄭文傑已獲釋回港<br />\n<br />\n英國駐港總領事館職員Simon Cheng（譯音鄭文傑）本月8日由深圳乘高鐵返港，其間與家人失去聯絡，其後確認遭內地行政拘留15日。昨日（23日）是鄭文傑被扣查滿15日。名為「釋放Simon Cheng」的facebook專頁今早（24日）發帖文，稱鄭文傑已回港，家人希望他能先休息，暫不接受採訪。<br />\n<br />\n帖文稱︰「Simon已回港，感謝大家關心！Simon和家人均希望先休息安頓一下，暫時不接受採訪，請各位記者朋友先給他們一點空間，我們稍後會再作詳細說明。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190824/s00001/1566612858488/fb%E5%B0%88%E9%A0%81-%E8%8B%B1%E9%A0%98%E9%A4%A8%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E9%84%AD%E6%96%87%E5%82%91%E5%B7%B2%E7%8D%B2%E9%87%8B%E5%9B%9E%E6%B8%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190824%2Fs00001%2F1566612858488%2Ffb%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A0%2581-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E9%25A0%2598%25E9%25A4%25A8%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%2582%2591%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E7%258D%25B2%25E9%2587%258B%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%25B8%25AF&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLhAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=926481e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190824%2Fs00001%2F1566612858488%2Ffb%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A0%2581-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E9%25A0%2598%25E9%25A4%25A8%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2593%25A1%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%2582%2591%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E7%258D%25B2%25E9%2587%258B%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%25B8%25AF&h=49b77cf9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190824/s00001/1566612858488/fb%E5%B0%88%E9%A0%81-%E8%8B%B1%E9%A0%98%E9%A4%A8%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E9%84%AD%E6%96%87%E5%82%91%E5%B7%B2%E7%8D%B2%E9%87%8B%E5%9B%9E%E6%B8%AF</a>"}